title: Zimbabwe Gasoline Prices
description: Gasoline Prices in Zimbabwe decreased to 1.58 USD/Liter in October from 2.59 USD/Liter in September of 2022. Gasoline Prices in Zimbabwe averaged 1.40 USD/Liter from 2017 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 3.39 USD/Liter in March of 2019 and a record low of 0.46 USD/Liter in February of 2022. This page provides - Zimbabwe Gasoline Prices- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Zimbabwe Energy Regulatory Authority
